→ **Message is discarded/skip delivery** — just an acknowledgment

**2. If I include HEARTBEAT_OK in a normal reply:**
```javascript
if (!params.isHeartbeat && text?.includes("HEARTBEAT_OK")) {
  const stripped = stripHeartbeatToken(text, { mode: "message" });
